Christ, I don't know how I'm missing this stuff, especially given how many times I've listened to this album! (To be fair, Wall Street isn't one of my favorite tracks on here.) Sorry, and thanks for pointing it out.

But I wonder, do you know what causes those skipping errors? This week I've got five albums with that stuff (Drop Gloss, Feel It Break, Microcastle, The Flying Club Cup and Burst Apart)... Anyway I already found an impeccable version of this album too. Thanks for the early leaks anyways!

I honestly have no idea why that happens from time to time. I guess it's the price we pay for getting the music early at no charge! (It goes without saying that I don't leak these albums myself; I just find them elsewhere and post them here.)
